data.description: Stunning two story home with four bedrooms and three bathrooms.  Finished basement that could serve as playroom, work out room or TV room.... Use your imagination.  Private back yard with lush, mature landscaping.  Three car garage for extra storage space.  Open concept with vaulted ceilings.  Formal Dining Room with niche and main floor laundry room. Family room with gas fireplace for cozy Colorado days.  All the appliances are included.  All rooms are generously sized for entertaining friends and family.  REAL hard wood floors!  Cherry Creek Schools and easy access to E470 for commutes.   Located in the desirable sub division of Encore at Seven Hills.  Come make this your forever home.  This home has so much room to grow in.  Over 3600 FINISHED square feet.  Close to Southlands shopping.  Hop and skip to E470 for quick commute to DIA.  Seller says "make offer".
